duck: Protozoology is the study of protozoan, the "animal-like" protists.
protozoology definition: a branch of zoology dealing with protozoans.

wiki.text:
'Protozoology' is the study of protozoan, the "animal-like" (i.e., motile and
heterotrophic) protists. This term has become dated as our understanding of the
evolutionary relationships of the eukaryota has improved.
wiki.title: protozoology
